1
00:01:28,840 --> 00:01:29,440
Linglong,

2
00:01:31,840 --> 00:01:33,240
how should I choose?

3
00:01:39,880 --> 00:01:40,680
Mr. Xu,

4
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:41,520
here is a letter for you.

5
00:01:41,520 --> 00:01:42,979
It arrived three days ago.

6
00:01:43,479 --> 00:01:45,680
The official seal of the Beiyang Fleet.

7
00:01:46,440 --> 00:01:48,500
Could it be related to the recent war?

8
00:01:57,960 --> 00:01:59,759
Recently, the Japanese army has been rampant,

9
00:01:59,759 --> 00:02:01,040
invading our vassal state.

10
00:02:01,040 --> 00:02:03,400
The coastal borders of Joseon are in a state of emergency.

11
00:02:03,400 --> 00:02:05,160
All naval officers, whether on leave

12
00:02:05,160 --> 00:02:06,280
or awaiting assignment,

13
00:02:06,280 --> 00:02:09,320
must immediately report for duty upon seeing this letter.

14
00:02:09,320 --> 00:02:10,080
Violators

15
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:12,140
will be dismissed and interrogated.

16
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:18,840
Linglong.

17
00:02:19,040 --> 00:02:19,720
Mr. Xu,

18
00:02:20,160 --> 00:02:21,320
why are you looking for the lady?

19
00:02:21,320 --> 00:02:21,680
Uncle Zhao,

20
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:23,240
I must see Linglong about something.

21
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:23,760
The lady

22
00:02:23,760 --> 00:02:25,290
is not available to see you.

23
00:02:26,640 --> 00:02:27,300
Uncle Zhao,

24
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:30,120
please give this wooden box to Linglong for me.

25
00:02:30,320 --> 00:02:30,800
Alas.

26
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:31,840
Please go back.

27
00:02:33,920 --> 00:02:34,560
Linglong,

28
00:02:34,720 --> 00:02:35,480
come out!

29
00:02:36,160 --> 00:02:37,160
I will be departing tomorrow.

30
00:02:37,160 --> 00:02:38,920
Mr. Xu, please stop shouting.

31
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:40,640
Madam has just passed away.

32
00:02:40,640 --> 00:02:42,400
The lady is grief-stricken.

33
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:45,079
You absolutely must not disturb her anymore.

34
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:55,440
Linglong.

35
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:59,260
Even though my heart is filled with thoughts of you,

36
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:01,720
with our country facing a crisis,

37
00:03:01,720 --> 00:03:03,240
how can I turn a blind eye?

38
00:03:04,760 --> 00:03:06,220
The country matters most.

39
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,920
When I defeat the Japanese army

40
00:03:07,920 --> 00:03:09,180
and return in triumph,

41
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:10,800
then,

42
00:03:11,520 --> 00:03:12,580
I will not fail you.

43
00:03:30,440 --> 00:03:31,160
Uncle Zhao.

44
00:03:32,200 --> 00:03:32,920
Miss,

45
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:37,120
while sorting Madam's belongings just now,

46
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:39,040
I found a letter she left for you.

47
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:47,560
Are you alright, Miss?

48
00:03:49,480 --> 00:03:51,610
I'll go busy myself with other things.

49
00:03:58,200 --> 00:03:59,200
Alas.

50
00:04:22,520 --> 00:04:23,920
My daughter Linglong,

51
00:04:24,280 --> 00:04:26,520
seeing this letter is like seeing me in person.

52
00:04:26,520 --> 00:04:28,680
If you are reading this letter,

53
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:30,680
I must have already passed away.

54
00:04:32,159 --> 00:04:33,690
My mortal ties are severed,

55
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:37,060
and I will reunite with your father in the netherworld.

56
00:04:37,880 --> 00:04:38,720
Long'er,

57
00:04:39,200 --> 00:04:40,440
in this life,

58
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:43,000
you are the one I am most reluctant to leave,

59
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:44,320
and the one I have wronged the most

60
00:04:44,320 --> 00:04:45,560
is also you.

61
00:04:46,280 --> 00:04:48,720
You have dressed as a boy since childhood.

62
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:50,200
I saw it,

63
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:51,880
and it broke my heart,

64
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:53,600
aching for you every day,

65
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:55,400
but there was no other way.

66
00:04:56,720 --> 00:04:59,850
Even though you have now restored your female identity,

67
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:01,960
I still feel I owe you in this life.

68
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:05,960
This regret remains unresolved.

69
00:05:05,960 --> 00:05:07,240
If there is a next life,

70
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:09,440
I will make it up to you.

71
00:05:13,080 --> 00:05:13,880
Long'er,

72
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:17,180
I know very well that improving black tea

73
00:05:17,400 --> 00:05:19,680
has always been your unfulfilled wish.

74
00:05:20,640 --> 00:05:22,360
Now foreign tea is flourishing,

75
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:24,000
and Keemun black tea is declining.

76
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:26,530
Improving black tea is more urgent than ever.

77
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:27,600
Recently,

78
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:29,960
the Hu family has been going through troubled times.

79
00:05:29,960 --> 00:05:31,360
But I beg you,

80
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:32,960
do not give up on this matter.

81
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:35,760
This is not just for making a living,

82
00:05:35,760 --> 00:05:38,400
but to win honor for the Chinese tea industry.

83
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:41,120
The amber in the cup

84
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:42,520
and the passage of time in the leaves

85
00:05:42,520 --> 00:05:45,440
are the foundation of the Hu family's livelihood,

86
00:05:45,960 --> 00:05:47,890
and also the way to prove yourself.

87
00:05:49,280 --> 00:05:50,200
Now,

88
00:05:50,440 --> 00:05:53,600
your mother's soul has followed your father's to the underworld.

89
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:55,320
From now on, you are all alone.

90
00:05:55,520 --> 00:05:56,880
You must guard against recklessness,

91
00:05:56,880 --> 00:05:58,840
act cautiously, and hide your edge.

92
00:05:58,840 --> 00:06:00,040
As for Zhinian,

93
00:06:00,320 --> 00:06:01,640
he is gentle and kind,

94
00:06:01,760 --> 00:06:03,090
upright and impartial,

95
00:06:03,120 --> 00:06:04,520
decent and keeps his promises.

96
00:06:04,520 --> 00:06:06,000
He is truly a good match.

97
00:06:06,880 --> 00:06:08,840
If you entrust your life to him,

98
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:10,640
your parents can

99
00:06:11,280 --> 00:06:13,560
rest in peace in the underworld.

100
00:06:16,520 --> 00:06:17,160
Linglong!

101
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:18,400
Mr. Xu,

102
00:06:18,400 --> 00:06:19,520
stop shouting.

103
00:06:19,520 --> 00:06:20,760
I have something important to talk to you about.

104
00:06:20,760 --> 00:06:21,400
Linglong,

105
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:22,280
come out!

106
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:24,380
I'm setting off tomorrow.

107
00:06:24,440 --> 00:06:25,280
Mr. Xu,

108
00:06:25,280 --> 00:06:26,400
the coastal war is intense.

109
00:06:26,400 --> 00:06:28,930
I don't know when we'll meet again after this.

110
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:31,160
Linglong, open the door!

111
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:32,440
Stop shouting!

112
00:06:32,760 --> 00:06:33,520
Linglong!

113
00:06:33,520 --> 00:06:35,480
My lady is already resting.

114
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:36,800
It's not convenient for her to see you.

115
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:38,159
Linglong, open the door!

116
00:06:38,159 --> 00:06:39,159
Linglong!

117
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:50,580
Uncle Zhao,

118
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:52,060
I'm going out for a bit.

119
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:53,200
Miss.

120
00:06:57,760 --> 00:06:58,600
Zhinian.

121
00:07:00,520 --> 00:07:01,680
Xu Zhinian!

122
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:03,840
What are you still lingering for?

123
00:07:03,840 --> 00:07:04,440
Let's go.

124
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:25,440
Nian,

125
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:27,620
when you get there,

126
00:07:27,760 --> 00:07:29,890
you must take good care of your health.

127
00:07:30,080 --> 00:07:32,810
Be sure to ask someone to send letters to me often.

128
00:07:33,240 --> 00:07:35,300
Even just to report that you are safe.

129
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:37,400
Don't worry,

130
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:38,159
Mother.

131
00:07:42,120 --> 00:07:42,920
Young Master,

132
00:07:42,960 --> 00:07:43,880
take care.

133
00:07:47,080 --> 00:07:47,520
Yes.

134
00:08:00,440 --> 00:08:02,040
I left a wooden box in my room.

135
00:08:02,320 --> 00:08:03,850
There are some things in it.

136
00:08:04,280 --> 00:08:05,740
Please check it carefully

137
00:08:06,240 --> 00:08:08,100
and help me give it to Hu Linglong.

138
00:08:08,840 --> 00:08:09,800
To Hu Linglong?

139
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:11,400
What is it?

140
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:14,450
You'll know when you see it.

141
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:18,640
Father,

142
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:21,240
Mother,

143
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:24,000
I'm leaving.

144
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:30,560
Nian,

145
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:31,860
when you come back,

146
00:08:31,960 --> 00:08:32,840
I'll make you

147
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:34,760
your favorite stinky mandarin fish

148
00:08:34,760 --> 00:08:36,080
and meatball pot.

149
00:08:39,120 --> 00:08:39,799
Father,

150
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:41,080
Mother,

151
00:08:43,039 --> 00:08:44,240
I have been unfilial.

152
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:50,400
Nian,

153
00:08:52,800 --> 00:08:54,480
a real man is born in the world

154
00:08:55,480 --> 00:08:57,810
and should put serving the country first.

155
00:08:58,440 --> 00:09:00,700
Remember the words loyalty and bravery.

156
00:09:05,920 --> 00:09:07,160
Set sail!

157
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:08,920
Seeing off guests!

158
00:09:09,800 --> 00:09:13,160
Have a safe journey!

159
00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:38,880
Xu Zhinian!

160
00:09:40,600 --> 00:09:42,160
Xu Zhinian.

161
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:46,120
Linglong.

162
00:09:56,880 --> 00:09:57,880
Xu Zhinian.

163
00:09:58,840 --> 00:09:59,640
Catch this.

164
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:06,360
Zhinian.

165
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:09,160
I'll wait for you to come back

166
00:10:09,160 --> 00:10:11,290
and return the hairpin to me yourself.

167
00:10:14,280 --> 00:10:15,360
I'll wait for you.

168
00:11:11,840 --> 00:11:12,560
Long'er.

169
00:11:12,560 --> 00:11:15,480
I attached the recipe for black tea pastry in this letter.

170
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:16,480
If one day

171
00:11:16,480 --> 00:11:18,200
you miss my handiwork,

172
00:11:18,200 --> 00:11:19,600
you can make it according to the recipe.

173
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:21,600
The fragrance of the pastry will fill the cup,

174
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:23,920
expressing my feelings.

175
00:11:30,120 --> 00:11:31,800
It's cool today.

176
00:11:35,400 --> 00:11:36,280
Hurry up,

177
00:11:36,280 --> 00:11:36,800
go.

178
00:11:42,120 --> 00:11:42,640
You,

179
00:11:42,640 --> 00:11:43,240
look up.

180
00:11:45,760 --> 00:11:46,360
It's him.

181
00:11:47,920 --> 00:11:48,960
Catch him!
